{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_110","type":"agent_message","text":"Implemented prompt 25 end to end. The left workspace pane is now a real chat surface with typed `assistant` / `user` / `system` / `action_echo` messages, timestamps, a multiline composer with submit handling, loading and disabled states, and a scroll-stable transcript backed by the session runtime store. The main wiring lives in [SessionChatPane.tsx](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/frontend/src/features/session/chat/SessionChatPane.tsx), [sessionChat.ts](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/frontend/src/features/session/chat/sessionChat.ts), and [SessionWorkspacePage.tsx](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/frontend/src/pages/session/SessionWorkspacePage.tsx). I also added a reusable [TextArea](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/frontend/src/shared/ui/primitives.tsx) primitive and committed the code checkpoint as `40b66cc` with message `feat(prompt-25): chat window foundation`.\n\nVerification passed:\n- `npm run lint`\n- `npm test -- src/features/session/chat/SessionChatPane.test.tsx src/pages/session/SessionWorkspacePage.test.tsx src/features/session/sessionRuntimeStore.test.ts src/shared/ui/primitives.test.tsx` (`14` tests passed)\n- `npm test` (`24` tests passed)\n- `npm run build`\n- Browser QA against the running Compose app, with screenshots at [chat-foundation-before-desktop.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/chat-foundation-before-desktop.png), [chat-foundation-after-desktop.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/chat-foundation-after-desktop.png), and [chat-foundation-after-mobile.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/chat-foundation-after-mobile.png)\n\nThe required reviewer summary was written last to [25-chat-window-foundation.summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/prompts/25-chat-window-foundation.summary.md)."}}
